and empirical\nnetworks verify the virtues of the articulated framework, opening the door to\nexploiting machine learning for understanding, detection, prediction, and\ncontrol of complex dynamical systems in general.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 12 Nov 2019 01:33:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-08"}
