 is derived\nfor the original jellium model as well as its simplified version with no\nbackground charge (charged wall surface with ``counter-ions only''). The\nobtained results are checked at the exactly solvable free-fermion coupling\n$\\Gamma=2$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 12 Nov 2019 13:35:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-29"}
